<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for Good Friday</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Apr 14, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <div class="org-center">

 <figure id="orge727937"> <img src="../images/posts/20170414-cross-mosaic.jpg" alt="20170414-cross-mosaic.jpg" width="100%"></img></figure></div>

 <p>
(Mosaic:  <i>Carrying the Cross of Christ</i> by Gabriel Loire) <sup> <a id="fnr.1" class="footref" href="#fn.1" role="doc-backlink">1</a></sup></p>

 <p>
It is a sign <br></br>
that we cannot <br></br>
really understand <br></br>
what it means <br></br>
for God to die, <br></br>
that we remember <br></br>
this day when <br></br>
truth and beauty <br></br>
hung upon a cross <br></br>
and we call it good.
</p>

 <p>
What our minds cannot comprehend, <br></br>
our words cannot express.
</p>

 <p>
So, we can do nothing <br></br>
but stand in silence <br></br>
before the glory <br></br>
and the horror <br></br>
of the cross.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>

